      <p class="case-body">I competed at the USA Junior Olympic National Championships three times, finishing in the top 0.014% of gymnasts nationwide. Trained 70+ hours a week, homeschooled for the sport. When I walked onto a trading desk at CIBC, I already knew how to perform when it counts.</p>
