      <p class="case-body">3.8 GPA at Northwestern. Semester at Sciences Po Paris. CFA Accelerate Scholar. Fluent in Mandarin. Kellogg research. Every piece reinforces the same story: someone who commits fully to whatever she takes on, and executes at a high level.</p>
